<TITLE>The Forbidden Game - Chapter 13</TITLE>
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Brian Inglis">
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFE0">
<!--webbot bot="Include"
u-include="../../_private/schaffer_logo.htm" tag="BODY" startspan
