<p><font size="5">The Joseph McNamara Collection</font></p>

<p>Joseph McNamara is a former police chief in Kansas City, Mo.
and San Jose, Ca.. He holds a doctorate in public administration
and is presently a research fellow at Stanford University's
Hoover Institution.</p>

